olds\r\nISO 9001-2008 in quality control management and is capable of\r\nmanufacturing<span> </span>corrugated pipe<span> </span>up to size of 88mm, spiral corrugated up to\r\nsize of 2500mm, and variety of manholes up to the size of 50000 litres. Neshgoastar\r\nPardis pipe products offer customized mechanical resistance of 16, 31.5 and 63\r\nKN/m2 according to EN13476-DIN16961-ISIRI 9116 standard.</p>', 2, 23, 'aboutUs', 'IMG_20100329_0335.JPG', '2010-04-27 22:01:07', '2010-05-09 18:54:12', 0),
